## Qualifications

SCRF is looking for someone who has *FILL IN THE DESIRED QUALIFICATIONS OF THIS ROLE*.

SCRF is looking for candidates who have:

* Clear communication skills and willingness to use chat, video, and email to coordinate
* Ability to work with a fully remote, globally distributed team
